projects.project_description: It is a desktop application that watch contents of youtube. It was developed using the api was provided by youtube.
we needed to measure performance for new features. To deal with a lot of data, I first stored it in redis and then stored it in db through cron.

Mobile coupons are wasting a lot of money. Because it disappears after the expiration date. I thought it would be nice if there was space to safely buy and sell mobile coupons.

I used information on sns accounts, mobile devices, and cybercrime inquiries for safety.
In order to expose products to Naver shopping, it needs to connect db-url. So I created admin page to manage it.

The menu of the dormitory restaurant was shown on the website, but there were many inconveniences. I thought it would be useful if there was something I could check as soon as I turned on the phone like a calendar.

I did not have access to the menu database, so I got a data through the web crawl. After that, the menu of dormitory was shown through webview and android widget function.
promotion date of company was registered automaticly to user. Because of that, participation rate was increased. Google and Naver provide related api.

It is difficult to know if the content on the web is trustworthy. So I wanted to make a fair space for trustworthy content.

It was developed using the data was provided by search engine through the open API or crawling.
Related posting api was not existed in daum. Daum had updated by my request, so I was able to add related daum service.
